     <li>Add and delete students records from the database</li>
     <li>Import student records to the local database from excel files</li>
     <li>Manage the system codes available in dropdown menus</li>
     <li>Export a list of all students into a PDF</li>
     <li>Perform adjudication on a selected term for all students in that term</li>
